    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "2018 sedan in fair condition. The exterior shows several noticeable scratches and a few small dings on the body panels. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear and some staining. While the car is operational, it may require some upcoming maintenance for optimal performance.",
      "price": 18500.0,
